name: graphene_django
description: Ampsight fork of graphene-django with local dependencies for high side access to GraphiQL.
readme: This package.json file lists the dependencies that are used by the GraphiQL interface, but the production bundles of each have been extracted and included in the repository (under js/ and css/). Some bundles have been renamed to avoid conflicts. See the README at the repo root for more information.
author: Avi Nerenberg
